node.text: In the sixth, and last, installment of Tommy Talks: #MovingForwardTogether Live Series with @CandaceReels, we join actor @Indyamoore to discuss visibility, inclusivity and equality for the LGBTQIA+ community. Inspired by the artworks of Rothko and Hopper, @clementphilippe_ gives a playful interpretation of our transitional bag collection with an emphasis on new colors of the season. 

“I like to build colorful and minimalistic compositions featuring accessories in a decontextualized way that flirt with abstraction. The chiaroscuro of the photographs gives depth to the scene, underlying the bag’s shapes and lines while creating rich color gradients that speak to the season.” 

The Modern Bar Bag is available now in Lofty Blue or Daring Scarlet. #TommyHilfiger
